selling.

Science doesn’t lie, politicians do. A
recent CBS poll found that 70 percent of
Americans favor decriminalization of med-
ical marijuana, considering its obvious ben-
eﬁts in medicine. There is, however, little
support on Capitol Hill.

Write to your congressman, senator
and president. Join NORML. Attend rallies
and smoke-outs. You don’t have to use mar-
ijuana to realize there is a great evil bearing
‘down on everyone’s rights and liberties. It
must be stopped — ﬁrst with the legaliza-
tion of marijuana for medical purposes.

That is the torch Lady Liberty carries
